    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to check out this absolute gem! It\u2019s in such incredible condition that it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s looking for someone who will love it just as much. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically perfect and ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you! Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
