    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s engineering peak, featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine. The powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver a high-revving, linear power delivery. This chassis has been meticulously preserved, featuring a factory-reinforced rear subframe and a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission with precise, positive gate engagement. Performance is further enhanced by the M Variable Differential Lock and a perfectly calibrated suspension geometry using aluminum control arms for reduced unsprung mass. The VANOS system has been professionally serviced and bulletproofed, ensuring the valvetrain operates with factory-new synchronization. Free of any oxidation or mechanical lash, this vehicle represents a concours-level investment for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Clean title. Zero accidents. Garage stored. Inspections welcome.",
      "price": 43000.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true automotive time capsule, this vehicle is in absolute showroom condition. The exterior features its original factory paint, which retains a deep, mirror-like luster completely free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the alloy wheels are pristine with no curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains in breathtaking condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the interior still carries a hint of that new-car scent. All electronics and mechanical systems function flawlessly, as this car has been meticulously maintained regardless of cost, with a full binder of service records included. It has been stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage under a soft cover and has never seen rain or snow. For the discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor, this is the definitive example.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
