      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty \u2013 it's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken incredible care of it, and it still has that fresh smell and a totally flawless finish inside and out. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure right now. Come take a look and see for yourself before someone else snaps it up!",
