    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 981-chassis Cayman S is a definitive example of mid-engine precision. It is powered by a 3.4L naturally aspirated flat-six featuring Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) and VarioCam Plus, delivering a linear power band that remains unrivaled. The drivetrain is anchored by a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a mechanical rear differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), providing active damping control that maintains optimal geometry under load. The braking system utilizes four-piston aluminum monobloc calipers over cross-drilled rotors with zero evidence of glazing or thermal stress. Meticulously preserved, the undercarriage is free of oxidation, and the DME report confirms zero overrevs in higher ranges. This is a mechanically flawless, investment-grade specimen for the purist collector.",
